title: Boy, 5, dies after choking on his school lunch as teachers tried to save him
text:
Boy, 5, dies after choking on his school lunch as teachers tried to save him By NEAL BAKER Comments A FIVE-year-old boy has died after choking on his lunch at school. 
Teachers and school staff had tried to resuscitate him after he passed out at Anlaby Primary School near Hull.
